  <brief_title>Perinatal Antiretroviral Intensification for PMTCT of HIV in Late Comers</brief_title>
  <acronym>PHPT-5</acronym>
  <official_title>PHPT-5 Second Phase: Perinatal Antiretroviral Intensification for the Prevention of Mother-to-child Transmission of HIV in Thai Women Having Received Less Than 8 Weeks of HAART During Pregnancy</official_title>
